A '''Beta Cruiser''' was a type of [[Battleship/Legends|battleship]] used by the [[Hapan Royal Navy]]. It was much smaller than the [[Nova-class battle cruiser|''Nova''-class battle cruiser]], but also more maneuverable. The Hapan fleet that fought in the [[Battle of Fondor]] contained many ships of this class, but few survived that engagement. One such cruiser as these was the ''[[Starsprite]]''.<ref name="Path1">[[The New Jedi Order: Dark Journey]]</ref>

